cs.LG, cs.DC, cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.AI

This paper is about scaling up deep neural networks using pipeline parallelism, which is a topic related to machine learning and specifically deep learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) since the paper deals with parallelism and distributed training. Additionally, the paper presents results on image classification and multilingual neural machine translation, which are tasks related to computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL, cs.AI), respectively.
